title: Moving to league from dota
body: Brand new to league moving from 4.7k Dota into ADC league looking for non toxic players of any skill level to level with and win games. IGN SteelySheepy

replies.body: I'm up to play whenever if you want ; KillVearn
Used to be 4k MMR in dota back the in day. Hit me up, I don't usually do normal's but I can certainly give you some tips and help you along :)
um im a bit salty when i have a bad day or when people are salty to me but im kind to new players <3 IGN nothing bots. and Welcome to OCE League
